<paragraph id="B680EB9CFBD655FF29B0BC303086631F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D20C5E8CC31FB56BB00454AC268832BD" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BOLIVIA. Santa Cruz, Velasco, 6-10 km N de San Rafael en el camino a San Miguel, 
<emphasis id="DFB9A7E74CE42439F96B15C0A4ADA4B4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">J.R.I. Wood &amp; D. Soto</emphasis>
27388 (holotype USZ; isotypes K, LPB).
</paragraph>
